data.description: Welcome to this stunning single-story home in one of Royal Palm's most popular communities- Bella Terra! The home welcomes you with a grand foyer with high ceilings, chandelier and 20-inch diagonal tile. It has an open floor concept and numerous upgrades throughout. The kitchen has been recently updated with quartz counters, Bosch stainless appliances, and reverse osmosis system. The primary suite has dual closets, a seamless glass shower, garden tub and double sink vanity. Both the primary suite and the kitchen/dining areas look out to the extended patio and fenced back yard with privacy hedge and plenty of room for a pool. The spacious garage has epoxy flooring, and the home is equipped with impact windows throughout for maximum hurricane protection and energy efficiency. This Lennar built gated community offers a desirable location just minutes to the interstate and shopping, resort style amenities and a low monthly HOA payment. Looking forward to welcoming you to this beautiful home!
